

Western Digital Technologies, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 1:09 PM ET
Technology Hardware, Storage and Peripherals

Company Overview of Western Digital Technologies, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Western Digital Technologies, Inc. develops and manufactures storage solutions that enable people to store, collect, access, and use digital information. The company offers various external storage products, such as desktop and portable drives for PCs; portable and desktop drives for Mac; and other storage drives for PCs and Mac. It also provides internal storage products, such as desktop, NAS, mobile, datacenter, surveillance, CE/AV, and workstation hard drives, as well as internal drive kits; personal cloud storage products; and home entertainment storage products, including media players, multimedia drives, DVR expander, and TV storage products. In addition, the company offers business so...
Western Digital Technologies, Inc. develops and manufactures storage solutions that enable people to store, collect, access, and use digital information. The company offers various external storage products, such as desktop and portable drives for PCs; portable and desktop drives for Mac; and other storage drives for PCs and Mac. It also provides internal storage products, such as desktop, NAS, mobile, datacenter, surveillance, CE/AV, and workstation hard drives, as well as internal drive kits; personal cloud storage products; and home entertainment storage products, including media players, multimedia drives, DVR expander, and TV storage products. In addition, the company offers business solutions, such as private cloud storage products, Windows storage servers, Windows servers, network backup solutions, guardian services, and other storage solutions. Its products are also used in business computers; digital video recorders at homes; and medical, military, aerospace, automotive, manufacturing, and telecommunications systems. The company serves consumers ranging from large companies to individuals. It offers its products through retailers/online E-tailers, SMB resellers, and distributors in North America, Africa, Asia, Europe, Latin America, the Middle East, and the Oceania. The company also offers its products, as well as cables, power supplies, carrying cases, and other accessories online. The company was incorporated in 1986 and is based in Irvine, California. Western Digital Technologies, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Western Digital Corporation.
Detailed Description


3355 Michelson DriveSuite 100Irvine, CA 92612United StatesFounded in 1986



